OverHistory.NewCommentry: Trent Boult to Aaron Finch Wicket
OverHistory.Commentry: Trent Boult bowling to Aaron Finch, good length ball, pitching outside off stump, Aaron Finch plays a defensive forward push WICKET Sunil Narine run out Shimron Hetmyer (Kolkata Knight Riders 0 Runs for 1 wickets)towards Extra Covers
OverHistory.UPDCommentry: First ball wicket for RR! Trent Boult bowling to Aaron Finch, good length ball, pitching outside off stump, Aaron Finch pushes the ball towards the extra covers fielder and runs for a quick single! Hetmyer is fast enough to get the ball and most importantly hits the stumps directly! Sunil Narine is way ahead from the crease and is out! WICKET!! Sunil Narine ro Shimron Hetmyer (Kolkata Knight Riders 0 Runs for 1 wicket)
